title: The List with Colleen Lopez 10.05.2017 - 09 PM
description:
Calling all sole sisters, tonight is all about shoes! We've got pumps, booties, clogs, over-the-knee boots, from brands like PureSole, Vince Camuto, Sam Edelman, Minnetonka, and more! Curator and host Colleen Lopez takes the guesswork out of style by showcasing her weekly favorites.

Prices shown on the previously recorded video may not represent the current price. Visit http://www.hsn.com to view the current selling price.
